gtypist: GNU Typist (also called gtypist) - an universal typing tutor.
gtypist:
gtypist: GNU Typist (also called gtypist) is an universal typing tutor.
gtypist: You can learn correct typing and improve your skills by practicing
gtypist: its exercises on a regular basis.
gtypist: 
gtypist: It comes with several typing tutorials: in Czech, English
gtypist: (Qwerty and Dvorak keyboard), Russian and Spanish, as well as
gtypist: simpler exercices in German, French and Norwegian.  It supports
gtypist: internationalization and already has an interface in Czech,
gtypist: English, Finnish, French, German and Spanish.
